videos.description: Ross Bowers pass is intercepted by USC's Jack Jones for a 15-yard return which leads to a Trojans' field goal.
videos.headline: Cal's QB Bowers throws interception

videos.description: Cal's Vic Enwere plows ahead for the first touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Bears' Enwere pushes through USC defense for TD

videos.description: Sam Darnold finds Tyler Petite for a 16-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Petite reaches his arm out for USC's first TD

videos.description: First, Cal''s Ross Bowers is sacked by USC's Christian Rector forcing a fumble. Then USC's Stephen Carr returns the favor by fumbling the ball away.
videos.headline: Cal and USC exchange fumbles

videos.description: Trojans' Sam Darnold's  pass is intercepted by Golden Bears' Josh Drayden to halt a USC drive.
videos.headline: USC's Darnold is picked off

videos.description: Golden Bears' Kanawai Noa makes a great catch with his forearms that would lead to a Cal field goal.
videos.headline: Cal's Noa makes great catch for 27 yards

videos.description: Golden Bears Head Coach Justin Wilcox talks about how Cal needs to do a better job tackling and be more consistent on drives.
videos.headline: Cal Head Coach Wilcox discusses how his team is competing hard

videos.description: Cal Golden Bears' mascot Oski trys to cool down with water and a bag of ice.
videos.headline: Cal mascot a hot mess on sideline

videos.description: Golden Bears' Ross Bowers fumbles and it is  recovered by USC's Uchenna Nwosu inside Cal's five.
videos.headline: USC forces Cal fumble for big turnover

videos.description: Trojans Stephen Carr extends the ball past the goal line for two-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: USC's Carr reaches out for TD

videos.description: Cal's Ross Bowers throws a bad interception as USC's Ykili Ross returns the ball 42 yards.
videos.headline: Bowers throws bad interception

videos.description: USC's Sam Darnold's pass is complete to Deontay Burnett for a four-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Trojans' Darnold finds Burnett in end zone for TD

videos.description: Cal's Ross Bowers throw is intercepted by Trojans' Jack Jones.
videos.headline: Bowers throws another interception in the second half

videos.description: Golden Bears' Ross Bowers pass is intercepted by Trojans' Chris Hawkins.
videos.headline: Bowers continues to struggle and throws third INT in second half

videos.description: Golden Bears Ross Bowers finds Jordan Veasy in the end zone for touchdown closing the gap 30-20.
videos.headline: Cal's Bowers pass complete to  Veasy forTD

videos.description: Clay Helton talks about how USC had a great second half, especially by defense, and how Stephen Carr stepped up.
videos.headline: Head Coach Helton discusses the great second half by USC

videos.description: Trojans' Sam Darnold discusses his performance against Cal and how great USC's defense played.
videos.headline: Sam Darnold reflects on his performance

videos.description: ESPN's Greg McElaroy and Dave Pasch discuss the turnovers in today's game and how USC made a comeback in the second half.
videos.headline: Miscues and turnovers abundant in USC - Cal game

videos.description: No. 5 USC forces six Cal turnovers while Sam Darnold throws for 223 yards, two touchdowns and an interception en route to the Trojans' 30-20 victory.
videos.headline: USC stops turnover-prone Cal
